GSD.description:
genirq/irqdesc: Don't try to remove non-existing sysfs files

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.15.86 by commit 93e3c803383a22c96c9a5589658809fed691aefc, it was introduced in version v4.9 by commit ecb3f394c5dba897d215a5422f1b363e93e2ce4e. For more details please see the references link.
